column5: WOW Thats CRAZY!!!!  I loved the 1 that took off like a rocket!  And the VW peels out lol
Seen that one before Brian but it's worth another look for sure.  You can see the truck driver run away to the left just after the accident.

Seen that one before Brian but it's worth another look for sure.  You can see the truck driver run away to the left just after the accident.  Yeah , the truck driver was probably the only one who knew what was coming, I like how the cop drove in and then backed out quickly when a missile came his way.

If you rewatch it over a few times, you see bottles flying. I missed some the first few times. This would explain why you dont transport them laying down driving through a plant on a fork lift as well. Knock off the head and WHAM OH. Lift off.

I wonder what he was carrying? Is that propane?  I seen this once in grande prarie with an unsecured load in a pick up(work truck) if I remember correctly it was a gas used for fracking. It was just one cylinder and it broke the tailgate at a stop and shot off like a rocket.  Thankfully nobody was hurt, but im sure the driver faced some wicked fines
